&lt;<span class="blue-dark">p</span>&gt;<span class="white">Enjoy unlimited access for 14 days. No credit card required.</span>&lt;/<span class="blue-dark">p</span>&gt;
</code></pre>
</span>
</li>
		<li>Edit the text of the form submit button from 'Sign Up' to 'Try it free' and change the Font Awesome icon.
