</code></pre>
</span></li>


		<li>Ensure that you have changed the email address in the form from <b>myname@gmail.com</b> to your own email address.
		<span class="inside-ol">&nbsp;</span>
		You can now save the <b>index.html</b> web page. You have finished updating it.</li>

		<li>In your <b>style.css</b> file, in the /* BROWSER RESETS */ section at the top, add the smooth-scrolling effect.
		
